video_title: 3 Signs Of Depression No One Tells You About - Dr Julie #Shorts
transcript:
his three signs of depression no one
tells you about number one is
disconnection from everyone around you
you might struggle to feel love even for
the people that mean most to you in the
world number two is numbness you might
not feel sadness at all you might feel
completely empty and numb
number three is those things that used
to come easy suddenly seems so hard so
simple things like getting in the shower
or leaving the house can demand so much
more energy than they used to
